> _Bad:_
> 
> ```js
> if (!a) {
>   a = 'foo';
> }
> ```
> 
> _Good:_
> 
> ```js
> a ||= 'foo';
> ```

Maybe we could also consider these:

```js
// a &&= 'foo'
if (a) a = 'foo';

// a ??= 'foo'
if (a == null) a = 'foo';

// a ??= 'foo'
if (a == undefined) a = 'foo';

// a ??= 'foo'
if (a === undefined || a === null) a = 'foo';
```

